      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. It runs smoothly and shows only minor signs of use, reflecting its careful previous ownership. If you're looking for a dependable, high-quality ride at a great value, this is the one for you!",
