    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone prioritizing functionality over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dings consistent with regular use, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention or small repairs in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for anyone needing a dependable daily commuter.",
